      %h1 Programming Contest
      %p
        Unleash all your creativity by building a web app of your choice using #{link_to 'Meteor-JS', 'http://www.meteor.com/', :target => :blank}, or #{ link_to 'Ruby on Rails', 'http://rubyonrails.org/', :target => :blank }.
        If you are able to #{ link_to 'build an app', 'http://railscasts.com/episodes/310-getting-started-with-rails', :target => :blank } using #{ link_to 'Ruby on Rails', 'http://guides.rubyonrails.org/', :target => :blank } you can earn bonus points.
