        #{ link_to 'Meteor-JS', 'http://www.meteor.com/', :target => :blank } will help you build a web app very easily.
        You will find complete documentation about it in the #{ link_to 'official documentation', 'http://docs.meteor.com/', :target => :blank } on website.
      %p
        If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <code>careers at finginie dot com</code>.
